6
00:00:29,630 --> 00:00:32,240
(Zhaozhao used to be an abused stray cat.)

7
00:00:33,840 --> 00:00:37,320
(Except for He Chen, it never lets anyone else
hold it)

8
00:01:10,720 --> 00:01:11,680
(He Chen.)

9
00:01:11,920 --> 00:01:12,840
(He Can.)

10
00:01:22,480 --> 00:01:23,520
How's King?

11
00:01:23,640 --> 00:01:24,480
He's fine.

12
00:01:24,720 --> 00:01:25,600
He's been playing with me.

13
00:01:25,920 --> 00:01:27,400
How do you know he's called "King"?

14
00:01:28,280 --> 00:01:29,360
That was the name

15
00:01:29,360 --> 00:01:31,120
He Chen gave him before.

16
00:01:39,160 --> 00:01:40,920
After He Chen and I adopted it,

17
00:01:41,200 --> 00:01:42,480
I changed its name

18
00:01:42,760 --> 00:01:43,600
to Zhaozhao.

19
00:01:44,040 --> 00:01:44,880
You...

20
00:01:45,680 --> 00:01:47,040
Who exactly are you?

21
00:01:54,080 --> 00:01:55,560
It's written clearly here.

22
00:01:55,900 --> 00:01:57,260
(King, happy 1st birthday.)
I'm not blind.

23
00:01:58,600 --> 00:01:59,760
You call me He Can one minute,

24
00:01:59,760 --> 00:02:01,000
and He Chen the next.

25
00:02:01,440 --> 00:02:03,080
Are you paranoid or something?

26
00:02:20,120 --> 00:02:21,360
You're too much.

27
00:02:50,520 --> 00:02:52,800
(Sorry, Hanxing.)

28
00:02:59,160 --> 00:03:00,000
Get lost.

29
00:03:00,040 --> 00:03:01,760
Bother me again and I'll teach you a lesson.

30
00:03:01,760 --> 00:03:03,300
(Santa Barbara, America)

31
00:03:12,720 --> 00:03:13,560
Can.

32
00:03:19,520 --> 00:03:21,200
Why did you come all the way here?

33
00:03:21,320 --> 00:03:22,160
Grandfather is ill.

34
00:03:22,760 --> 00:03:23,600
Come back with me.

35
00:03:23,920 --> 00:03:24,760
That's your grandfather,

36
00:03:24,760 --> 00:03:25,640
not mine.

37
00:03:26,080 --> 00:03:26,920
What?

38
00:03:27,200 --> 00:03:28,680
Can't lift the coffin by yourself?

39
00:03:29,080 --> 00:03:30,200
My leg is lame.

40
00:03:31,320 --> 00:03:32,160
I can't help you.

41
00:03:33,280 --> 00:03:34,280
We're family.

42
00:03:38,280 --> 00:03:39,120
Family?

43
00:03:39,960 --> 00:03:41,480
When my mom remarried,

44
00:03:41,480 --> 00:03:42,920
you all abandoned us.

45
00:03:43,680 --> 00:03:45,240
Where were you when she died?

46
00:03:46,240 --> 00:03:48,240
Where were you when Charles forced me
to learn the piano

47
00:03:48,240 --> 00:03:49,240
to earn performance fees?

48
00:03:51,040 --> 00:03:51,880
Huh?

49
00:03:52,080 --> 00:03:53,280
I didn't know you were living this hard.

50
00:03:53,640 --> 00:03:54,480
They all said you...

51
00:03:54,480 --> 00:03:55,320
What did they say?

52
00:03:55,800 --> 00:03:57,920
They said every time I called, it was
to ask for money?

53
00:03:57,920 --> 00:03:59,680
That was all Charles forcing me to call.

54
00:04:00,280 --> 00:04:01,280
You talk about family,

55
00:04:01,840 --> 00:04:03,320
but if you had thought of me earlier,

56
00:04:03,600 --> 00:04:05,320
my leg wouldn't be like this now.

57
00:04:15,720 --> 00:04:16,560
I'm sorry.

58
00:04:17,200 --> 00:04:18,960
Sorry doesn't solve anything, does it?

59
00:04:34,360 --> 00:04:35,200
Ahoge,

60
00:04:54,440 --> 00:04:55,840
give me one more chance, okay?

61
