When we were kids,

62
00:05:01,240 --> 00:05:02,400
I promised I'd protect you.

63
00:05:02,800 --> 00:05:04,000
This time, I won't go back on my word.

64
00:05:05,960 --> 00:05:06,800
Ahoge,

65
00:05:08,480 --> 00:05:09,600
come home with me.

66
00:05:23,880 --> 00:05:25,320
You look better with new clothes.

67
00:05:28,920 --> 00:05:30,960
I feel uncomfortable in this suit.

68
00:05:33,760 --> 00:05:34,600
By the way,

69
00:05:35,040 --> 00:05:35,880
take this.

70
00:05:37,840 --> 00:05:39,200
Dad left it for you.

71
00:05:39,200 --> 00:05:40,520
He said it could bring you good luck.

72
00:05:40,840 --> 00:05:41,720
I was afraid of losing it,

73
